### count all unread notifications
GET http://localhost:8080/notification/count/unread
Content-Type: application/json

### mark all unread notifications as read
GET http://localhost:8080/notification/mark-all-read
Content-Type: application/json

### get all unread notifications with pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/notification/list/unread
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 1,
    "limit": 10
}